Ibid., Seventy-fourth Session, Supplement No. 46 (A/74/46), chap. II, sect. C. and encourages the Committee, over its coming sessions, to continue to work towards implementing strategies to support its long-term efforts to serve the scientific community, as well as wider audiences;
